Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.61,Cartello BASE -X-,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.5\fad(450,0)\fs17\shad0\bord0\fnTrebuchet MS\pos(449.998,320.677)}Maestra della scuola elementare Haido\N (Ex insegnante di Ran e Sonoko)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:59.61,Cartello BASE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H803F29&\fad(450,0)\an7\blur1.3\bord0\shad0\fscx100\fscy100\pos(195.687,303.007)\p1}m -107 -66 l 101 -66 101 18 -107 18
